Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四艘戰艦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每艘方向都各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他不要帶護衛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然開出四艘戰艦來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是墮落至極
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方艦隊如何行動？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要隨他耍小聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天城出來的艦隊動作出奇的慢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方確實在邀請我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像還有別的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞恐怕想讓亞瑟斯伯去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯伯人格有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上層人物是想藉此除去累贅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從放著兄長哲力胥不用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而派伊德里斯迎接也能看出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵人緣也真差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意放任亞瑟斯被我們殺死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯再替他報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一舉兩得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是泰坦尼亞的慣用伎倆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回來吧 亞瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩兒也想見母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,923)\fad(500,500)}泰莉莎·泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}テリーザ・タイタニア
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不讓我看看你？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看你有精神的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信號不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是對你擔心得不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩兒很快就到天城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您暫時忍耐 母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不去接他？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是藩王殿下的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.99,0:09:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不擔心弟弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯提耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還看不到伊德里斯卿的艦隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說已經離開天城了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他磨蹭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要被伯爵逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題在於 哪艘船是真貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.94,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要靜觀其變
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方自然會露出馬腳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.50,0:10:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 等著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我也有些等得不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為他的鼻子夠靈光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能由我們這邊出手幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦知道亞瑟斯的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他馬上就會發動襲擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時就是他的末日了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功之時請務必…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的艦隊趕到之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.07,0:11:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到伯爵閣下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這傢伙沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在向伊德里斯的艦隊發信號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是泰坦尼亞貴族專用的通信編碼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 動手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮 準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近防禦 準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封閉隔斷牆 戰鬥準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時可以戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的艦隊也加入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你負責指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 亞瑟斯·泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後方發現敵艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離1200
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡航艦 總數15
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徑直向本艦衝來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為宇宙塵埃的會是方修利一行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 敵人可不只一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區海賊 不管怎麼聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下所搭乘的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.82,0:12:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正是泰坦尼亞引以為豪的戰艦極光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯閣下也很快就會趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的指揮權能交給在下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把方修利殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮門 開啟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦倫科夫 先攻擊引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 敵艦引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1022,923)\fad(500,500)}米哈伊爾·瓦倫科夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1022,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミハエル・ワレンコフ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一機關室 嚴重損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法維持戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把全部炮火擊中到敵艦頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一舉擊潰他們！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦隊 向兩翼展開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 會被追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火 開火 開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.12,0:14:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的艦隊攻擊側翼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 右舷推進器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮 發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷推進器 受損
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我們動彈不得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯提耶 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點程度 對極光來說無關痛癢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝魯提耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,180度掉頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊後方敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利肯定就在那上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥中要把腹部暴露給敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方不知道什麼叫戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,側面完全暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李艦隊 左右夾擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主推進器 停止運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二 第三 第四 第六炮塔嚴重損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯艦隊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯艦隊沒有任何動作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿真會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接伊德里斯閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接不上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來極光受損嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.51,0:16:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可能被擊沉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候只要替他們報仇就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬可悲的羔羊們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方一開始就有這個打算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 亞瑟斯閣下他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管他 指揮官是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火 開火 狠狠地打！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船怎麼能被他們擊沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要親手幹掉方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓伊德里斯卿認同我的實力！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會輸嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦停止攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊由我親自動手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標 戰艦極光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯·泰坦尼亞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞瑟斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極光 被擊沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利艦的識別信號是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.04,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被敵方的欺瞞信號妨礙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.78,0:20:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知哪個是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法分辨方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥時時都要考慮退路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星艾曼塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.46,0:20:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星エーメンタール
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該是開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 莉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此仇不共戴天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將方修利視為泰坦尼亞的公敵！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.49,0:21:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.89,0:21:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾真不會照顧花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅長這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要像對待女生一樣溫柔就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 就算妳這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 連這個都不會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能永遠看著這種景象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿和哲力胥卿都視方修利為眼中釘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.15,0:22:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠他一個人情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚要還的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.48,0:22:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方修利來說 宇宙越來越小了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時此刻 泰坦尼亞榮華依舊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.69,0:22:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多數人還無法想像它會有終結的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和公主在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.57,0:24:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺亞瑟斯的死離我如此遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.43,0:24:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的周圍也發生了異變
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.78,0:24:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.05,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(694,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}盧塔西的動亂


